Song Ah!

278
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:18,260
Solve the misunderstanding with Hyeon Ho.

279
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:37,500
Song Ah.

280
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:41,790
There was no such thing, I'm saying the truth.

281
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,900
Please believe me.

282
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:54,480
I believe you.

283
00:25:56,980 --> 00:25:58,980
I do.

284
00:26:01,950 --> 00:26:03,970
But...

285
00:26:08,810 --> 00:26:12,430
