286
00:26:12,430 --> 00:26:16,200
I mean, in between those times...

287
00:26:16,990 --> 00:26:22,760
Is there any room for me to go in?

288
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:37,530
I'll wait for you... I'm waiting for you, but...

289
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:41,740
