311
00:28:48,760 --> 00:28:56,070
♫   Come back to me a bit less late   ♫

312
00:28:56,070 --> 00:29:00,730
    
 ♫   Even these tears that are falling  ♫

313
00:29:00,730 --> 00:29:04,780
♫   Will become   ♫

314
00:29:04,780 --> 00:29:11,460
♫   Part of my last farewell to you, take care.    ♫

315
00:29:11,460 --> 00:29:15,110
♫   Only one, just one thing   ♫

316
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:18,800
    
 ♫   I hope you won't forget  ♫

317
00:29:18,800 --> 00:29:25,510
♫   The one who loved you   ♫

318
00:29:34,390 --> 00:29:35,590
Yeah, Eun Ji?

319
00:29:35,590 --> 00:29:38,800
